20hammock%20of%20muscles%20that%20control%20how%20well%20we%20can%20urinate%2C%20perform%20a%20bowel%20movement%2C%20and%20have%20sex.%20This%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpelvic-floor-exercises-beyond-kegels-for-any-age-2020-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epelvic%20floor%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20operating%20properly%2C%20it%20sits%20largely%20unnoticed%2C%20helping%20thanklessly%20to%20facilitate%20these%20bodily%20functions%20throughout%20the%20course%20of%20each%20day.%20But%2C%20if%20the%20pelvic%20floor%20muscles%20become%20too%20tight%20or%20too%20loose%2C%20chaos%20can%20ensue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20what%20happened%20to%20Adam%20Gvili%20when%20he%20was%20in%20his%20early%2020s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22460%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22pelvis%20headshot%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687023f485e81483682dcc8c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAdam%20Gvili%20is%20a%20physical%20therapist%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20Pelvis%20NYC.%3Cp%3EPranto%20Podder%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20went%20like%2020%20times%20a%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Gvili%2C%20now%20a%20physical%20therapist%20treating%20pelvic%20floor%20issues%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20referring%20to%20his%20frequent%20urge%20to%20pee%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20most%20common%20symptoms%20of%20hypertonic%20pelvic%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20US%20National%20Institutes%20of%20Health's%20Pelvic%20Floor%20Disorders%20Network%2C%20up%20to%20one%20in%20five%20women%20will%20have%20surgery%20for%20a%20pelvic%20floor%20disorder%20at%20some%20point%20in%20her%20lifetime%2C%20and%20even%20more%20women%20%E2%80%94%20about%2032%25%20%E2%80%94%20will%20have%20some%20sort%20of%20diagnosed%20pelvic%20floor%20disorder.%20The%20number%20of%20men%20with%20chronic%20pelvic%20pain%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%20about%20half%20that%2C%20around%2016%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPelvic%20floor%20experts%20told%20BI%20these%20men%20are%20often%20suffering%20in%20the%20shadows.%20Almost%20no%20one%20is%20talking%20about%20the%20male%20pelvic%20floor%2C%20due%20to%20a%20mix%20of%20shame%2C%20a%20lack%20of%20awareness%2C%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20getting%20a%20diagnosis%20typically%20involves%20a%20long%20process%20of%20elimination%20with%20specialists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20patients%20quietly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aptapelvichealth.org%2Fptlocator%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efind%20PTs%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20Gvili%20on%20Reddit%20or%20through%20frantic%20Google%20searching%2C%20he%20said.%20Others%20might%20hear%20him%20on%20a%20podcast%2C%20or%20are%20referred%20from%20a%20urologist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20they%20have%20this%20urge%20and%20frequency%20to%20go%2C%20it's%20like%2C%20'Do%20I%20have%20to%20go%3F%20Should%20I%20go%3F%20Wait%2C%20I'm%20not%20sure.%20I%20already%20went%20like%2020%20minutes%20ago.%20Does%20that%20mean%20I%20really%20have%20to%20go%3F'%20And%20that's%20just%20for%20urination%2C%26quot%3B%20Gvili%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20imagine%20how%20much%20in%20your%20head%20you%20can%20get.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2282641808-f381-4531-9d2f-12ce6744c06f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESymptoms%20of%20an%20overactive%20pelvic%20floor%20in%20men%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20needing%20to%20pee%20often%2C%20common%20tell-tale%20signs%20of%20a%20pelvic%20floor%20in%20panic%20mode%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EShooting%20pain%20in%20the%20rectum%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EErectile%20dysfunction%20(ED)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPremature%20ejaculation%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EConstipation%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGroin%20pain%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETesticular%20pain%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20like%20the%20muscle%20pops%20up%20and%20says%2C%20'Hey%2C%20I'm%20the%20problem%2C'%26quot%3B%20physical%20therapist%20Karen%20Brandon%2C%20president%20of%20the%20International%20Pelvic%20Pain%20Society%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20more%20common%20is%20that%20men%20will%20experience%20symptoms%20of%20urgency%20and%20difficulty%20urinating%20and%20some%20random%20strange%20pains%20in%20their%20penis%20or%20their%20scrotum.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2299a43e59-19cd-4833-b5c3-15cfa5deb570%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EStress%20is%20not%20the%20only%20reason%20men%20can%20develop%20an%20over-toned%20pelvic%20floor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20myriad%20reasons%20that%20a%20pelvic%20floor%20can%20become%20tight%20and%20overengaged.%20Sometimes%2C%20it's%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20some%20people%2C%20they%20tense%20their%20pelvic%20floor%20when%20that%20%5Bstress%5D%20happens%26quot%3B%20Gvili%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpelvis.nyc%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPelvis%20NYC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said.%20Tensing%20and%20tightening%20those%20muscles%20can%20also%20be%20a%20response%20to%20anxiety%2C%20or%20sexual%20trauma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20of%20the%20cases%20he%20sees%20are%20linked%20to%20stress%2C%20though.%20He%20says%20there%20are%20a%20fair%20number%20of%20%26quot%3Btype%20B%20guys%20here%20that%20are%20way%20chill%20and%20have%20this%26quot%3B%20for%20other%20reasons.%20Older%20men%20can%20develop%20a%20hypertonic%20pelvic%20floor%20after%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiagnosed-with-prostate-cancer-at-49-how-changed-my-life-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprostatectomy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20could%20be%2C%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20men%2C%20masturbating%20too%20many%20times%2C%20it%20could%20be%20after%20squatting%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ffitness%2Fdeadlift-form%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edeadlifting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20there's%20many%20reasons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMale%20pelvic%20floor%20issues%20can%20also%20be%20spurred%20by%20an%20infection%20or%20injury%20to%20the%20area%2C%20even%20a%20%26quot%3Breally%20bad%20bowel%20movement%2C%26quot%3B%20Brandon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20happens%20is%20your%20pelvic%20floor%20muscle%20then%20starts%20to%20guard%20and%20get%20protective.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2282b18b59-dfc1-43a7-be22-bebed7500bd3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELift%20heavy%20weights%2C%20stretch%2C%20and%20spend%20less%20time%20on%20the%20toilet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20Gvili%20said%2C%20there's%20not%20a%20ton%20that%20men%20can%20do%20to%20prevent%20the%20pelvic%20floor%20from%20going%20into%20overdrive.%20Of%20course%2C%20maintaining%20a%20good%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foptimize-workout-personal-trainer-red-green-flags-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexercise%20routine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20staying%20flexible%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fbreathing-exercises%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebreathing%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20stress%2C%20and%20time%20for%20relaxation%2C%20those%20all%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20work%20endeavors%20to%20help%20people%20pay%20less%20attention%20to%20their%20pelvic%20floor%2C%20and%20let%20%26quot%3Byour%20body's%20natural%20mechanism%26quot%3B%20operate%20automatically%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221890%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22pelvis%20at%20work%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687023f43d5881a51c1d1d56%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222645%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BThese%20muscles%20need%20to%20learn%20that%20they%20can%20relax%2C%26quot%3B%20Gvili%20said.%3Cp%3EPranto%20Podder%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20goal%20is%20to%20decrease%20your%20awareness%20to%20a%20certain%20area%20of%20the%20body%2C%26quot%3B%20Gvili%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20as%20simple%20as%20'just%20do%20some%20kegels.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20it's%20the%20engagement%20and%20then%20release%20of%20the%20pelvic%20floor%20throughout%20the%20day%20that%20will%20help%20keep%20it%20healthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrandon%20imagines%20the%20pelvic%20floor%20like%20a%20set%20of%20saloon%20doors%20that%20can%20swing%20both%20ways%3A%20lifting%20and%20pulling%20in%2C%20much%20like%20you%20would%20for%20a%20kegel%2C%20but%20also%20doing%20the%20opposite%2C%20by%20dropping%20and%20releasing%2C%20telescoping%20the%20anus%20to%20push%20towards%20the%20floor%2C%20almost%20like%20you're%20about%20to%20pass%20gas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20best%20things%20Gvili%20recommends%20for%20maintaining%20a%20healthy%20pelvic%20floor%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-lifting-burns-fat-faster-than-cardio-trainer-advice-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estrength%20training%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLift%20heavy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSquats%2C%20dead%20lifts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222120%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close%20up%20of%20a%20man's%20arms%20and%20legs%20as%20he%20prepares%20to%20do%20a%20heavy%20deadlift%20exercise.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd14b36fcb546d2d4b9a12%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStrength%20training%20is%20good%20for%20the%20pelvic%20floor%2C%20just%20don't%20overdo%20it.%3Cp%3EWestend61%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20you%20have%20to%20be%20careful.%20Brandon%20stresses%20that%20maintaining%20%26quot%3Bgood%20form%26quot%3B%20for%20your%20strength%20training%20is%20essential%2C%20to%20ensure%20you're%20not%20%26quot%3Bbiasing%20a%20certain%20muscle%20and%20overusing%20the%20one%20that's%20connected%20to%20the%20pelvic%20floor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMen%20with