2F122403260.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20get%20your%20manager%20to%20tell%20you%20if%20a%20layoff%20is%20coming%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20in%20business%20suit%20presenting%20pink%20slip%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68715770f748d8c055f57c37%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20you're%20worried%20about%20layoffs%2C%20workplace%20experts%20say%20it%20can%20be%20wise%20to%20subtly%20raise%20the%20subject%20with%20your%20manager.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Ava%20Horton%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECertain%20subtle%20workplace%20signs%20may%20mean%20layoffs%20are%20on%20the%20horizon%2C%20say%20career%20experts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20option%20is%20to%20ask%20your%20manager%20%E2%80%94%20either%20directly%20or%20indirectly.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20good%20to%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetworking-important-new-job-economy-ai-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enetwork%20regularly%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20keep%20an%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcant-get-job-what-to-never-always-include-resume-hiring-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eup-to-date%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20regardless%20of%20what%20your%20manager%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20weeks%20leading%20up%20to%20his%20second%20layoff%20in%20less%20than%20a%20year%2C%20Isaac%20Simon%20began%20to%20notice%20some%20eerily%20familiar%20changes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20again%2C%20the%20content%20manager%20was%20getting%20less%20attention%20from%20leaders%20than%20when%20he%20joined%20the%20company%2C%20a%20mobile%20game%20developer%2C%20and%20long-term%20assignments%20were%20getting%20shelved.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20he%20was%20let%20go%20last%20month%2C%20Simon%2C%20a%2037-year-old%20Boston%20native%20living%20in%20Amsterdam%2C%20said%20he%20wasn't%20surprised%2C%20though%20he%20regrets%20that%20he%20didn't%20work%20up%20the%20nerve%20to%20approach%20his%20manager%20about%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20wish%20I%20had%20just%20asked%2C%26quot%3B%20Simon%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20adding%20that%20if%20he'd%20gotten%20a%20clear%20answer%2C%20he%20would've%20tried%20finding%20new%20ways%20to%20add%20value%20or%20started%20looking%20for%20a%20new%20job%20sooner.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecent-company-layoffs-laying-off-workers-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELayoffs%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20have%20become%20so%20rampant%20in%20some%20industries%20that%20people%20who've%20received%20multiple%20pink%20slips%20say%20they've%20learned%20to%20recognize%20common%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foffice-paranoia-layoffs-ai-job-security-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esigns%20of%20impending%20job%20cuts%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Yet%20these%20indicators%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20the%20loss%20of%20a%20major%20client%20or%20a%20sudden%20increase%20in%20closed-door%20meetings%20%E2%80%94%20aren't%20foolproof.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20get%20a%20better%20sense%20of%20what's%20really%20going%20on%2C%20workplace%20experts%20say%20it%20can%20make%20sense%20to%20subtly%20raise%20the%20subject%20to%20your%20manager%20or%20a%20trusted%20leader.%20Though%20the%20move%20isn't%20guaranteed%20to%20work%2C%20confirmation%20can%20provide%20relief%20or%20soften%20the%20blow%20of%20a%20future%20dismissal.%20It%20might%20also%20give%20you%20more%20time%20to%20find%20a%20new%20role%20before%20the%20hammer%20officially%20comes%20down.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bd326cb5-b07f-455e-9eb0-7a7c6384906d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20to%20ask%20your%20manager%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20way%20to%20get%20a%20manager%20to%20dish%20is%20by%20posing%20an%20indirect%20question%2C%20said%20Nicola%20Worthy%2C%20an%20HR%20consultant%20in%20Charlotte%2C%20N.C.%20This%20could%20be%3A%20Is%20now%20a%20good%20time%20for%20me%20to%20buy%20a%20new%20home%20or%20a%20new%20car%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20higher-ups%20might%20be%20barred%20from%20spilling%20the%20beans%20outright%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20always%20a%20way%20of%20signaling%26quot%3B%20that%20a%20layoff%20is%20coming%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWorthy%20recalled%20how%20a%20former%20HR%20colleague%20once%20told%20her%3A%20%26quot%3B'None%20of%20us%20should%20be%20shopping%20for%20a%20boat%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%20That%20was%20code%20for%20%26quot%3Bit%20might%20be%20time%20to%20dust%20off%20the%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20She%20got%20the%20boot%20about%20a%20month%20later.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20strategy%20is%20to%20inquire%20about%20internal%20career%20opportunities%2C%20said%20Amanda%20Goodall%2C%20an%20independent%20provider%20of%20workforce%20intelligence%20for%20investors%20and%20executives.%20Frame%20the%20conversation%20around%20wanting%20to%20make%20yourself%20more%20of%20an%20asset%20to%20the%20company%20such%20as%20by%20asking%20what%20you%20can%20do%20to%20set%20yourself%20up%20for%20a%20promotion%20or%20move%20into%20a%20more%20senior%20role.%20Then%20pay%20close%20attention%20to%20the%20person's%20body%20language%20and%20choice%20of%20words.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20get%20a%20really%20strong%20feel%20on%20how%20receptive%20they%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Goodall%2C%20whose%20business%20is%20called%20The%20Job%20Chick.%20%26quot%3BTheir%20confidence%20will%20be%20up%20or%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dd51ed4d-6703-4d0f-aa36-d593ab37f9a8%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20may%20get%20mixed%20results%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMatt%20Dinovo%2C%20a%2049-year-old%20information-technology%20professional%20in%20Delaware%2C%20Ohio%2C%20has%20experienced%20three%20layoffs%20since%202019.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbout%20a%20month%20before%20the%20first%2C%20he%20said%20he%20was%20surprised%20and%20grateful%20when%20his%20manager%20informed%20him%20during%20a%20one-on-one%20that%20his%20job%20was%20on%20the%20chopping%20block.%20The%20manager%20explained%20that%20the%20company%20was%20planning%20layoffs%20and%20he%20was%20on%20a%20list%20of%20people%20who'd%20be%20getting%20axed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BSo%20when%20it%20happened%2C%20it%20wasn't%20a%20big%20deal%2C%26quot%3B%20Dinovo%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20second%20layoff%20in%202023%20didn't%20go%20as%20well.%20Shortly%20beforehand%2C%20he%20asked%20his%20superior%20outright%20if%20he%20was%20a%20target%20for%20cuts%20because%20he'd%20been%20made%20aware%20that%20he'd%20have%20to%20let%20go%20of%20some%20people%20on%20his%20team.%20Dinovo%20was%20told%20no%2C%20but%20that%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20wrong.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20always%20believe%20what%20you%20hear%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20third%20layoff%2C%20which%20occurred%20in%20December%2C%20Dinovo%20had%20already%20sensed%20trouble%20was%20afoot%20since%20his%20employer's%20business%20model%20was%20changing.%20This%20time%20he%20asked%20his%20boss%20what%20he%20could%20do%20to%20stay%20relevant.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BLeadership%20didn't%20show%20interest%20in%20trying%20to%20help%20me%20find%20a%20new%20role%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20which%20he%20took%20to%20mean%20he%20was%20likely%20on%20his%20way%20out.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20enough%20of%20an%20awareness%20of%20the%20situation%20when%20it%20happened.%20I%20wasn't%20blindsided.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a5a28aa4-e84f-4fa0-b73d-712b2ead4922%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPreparing%20for%20an%20uncertain%20future%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECareer%20experts%20say%20it's%20wise%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetworking-important-new-job-economy-ai-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enetwork%20regularly%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20keep%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcant-get-job-what-to-never-always-include-resume-hiring-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eup-to-date%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20case%20a%20layoff%20strikes%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20scramble%20if%20it%20happens.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20advice%20is%20especially%20salient%20at%20the%20moment.%20U.S.-based%20employers%20announced%20247%2C256%20job%20cuts%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%2C%20up%2039%25%20from%20a%20year%20ago%20and%20the%20highest%20total%20for%20the%20April-through-June%20period%20since%202020%2C%20according%20to%20outplacement%20and%20coaching%20firm%20Challenger%2C%20Gray%20%26amp%3B%20Christmas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECompanies%20are%20making%20cuts%20in%20response%20to%20a%20range%20of%20factors%2C%20from%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-stock-market-inflation-outlook-corporate-earnings-morgan-stanley-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%20administration's%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20foreign%20imports%20and%20higher%20inflation%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ceos-talk-ai-job-impact-employees-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20tools%20that%20can%20handle%20some%20tasks%20in%20lie