Cli%3EInvestors%20have%20come%20to%20see%20Trump's%20more%20extreme%20trade%20policies%20as%20bluffs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20without%20financial%20markets%20to%20check%20Trump%2C%20will%20the%20trade%20backfire%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGMO's%20Ben%20Inker%20says%20markets'%20faith%20that%20Trump%20always%20chickens%20out%20could%20backfire.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBuying%20the%20dip%20during%20recent%20tariff%20volatility%20has%20been%20a%20profitable%20strategy%20this%20year%2C%20but%20will%20the%20so-called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaco-trade-trump-tariffs-investors-stock-market-japan-south-korea-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETACO%20trade%3C%2Fa%3E%20backfire%20on%20bullish%20investors%20who%20are%20confident%20that%20the%20president%20will%20always%20back%20down%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20didn't%20take%20long%20for%20investors%20to%20figure%20out%20that%20Trump%20doesn't%20always%20mean%20what%20he%20says%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20trade%20policy.%20The%20TACO%20trade%20%E2%80%94%20short%20for%20%26quot%3BTrump%20always%20chickens%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20phrase%20coined%20by%20the%20Financial%20Times'%20Robert%20Armstrong%20to%20describe%20Trump's%20habit%20of%20backing%20away%20from%20proposals%20that%20roil%20markets%E2%80%94%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20have%20started%20not%20to%20take%20Trump%20so%20seriously%2C%20believing%20his%20more%20extreme%20policy%20proposals%2C%20like%20blanket%20tariffs%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-backs-off-firing-jerome-powell-markets-rally-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efiring%20the%20Chairman%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%2C%20are%20just%20a%20bluff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Ben%20Inker%2C%20the%20co-head%20of%20asset%20allocation%20at%20GMO%2C%20argues%20that%20this%20approach%20may%20backfire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarkets%20have%20acted%20as%20a%20check%20on%20Trump%20this%20year.%20The%20president%20paused%20tariffs%20in%20April%20after%20historic%20sell-offs%20in%20both%20stocks%20and%20bonds%2C%20and%20he's%20backed%20down%20from%20ideas%20like%20firing%20Jerome%20Powell%20as%20Fed%20chief%20after%20markets%20balked%20at%20the%20prospect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20with%20investors%20seemingly%20less%20willing%20to%20sell%20after%20every%20bold%20proposal%20Trump%20makes%2C%20he%20may%20have%20little%20incentive%20to%20back%20off%20from%20his%20trade%20war%2C%20which%20he%20has%20ramped%20up%20again%20this%20week.%20He%20recently%20announced%2025%25%20tariffs%20on%20Japan%20and%20South%20Korea%2C%20and%2050%25%20tariffs%20on%20Brazil%2C%20and%2035%25%20on%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStocks%20dipped%20on%20Friday%2C%20but%20it%20was%20nothing%20like%20the%20sell-off%20in%20April%2C%20despite%20some%20tariffs%20announced%20in%20the%20week%20being%20steeper%20than%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we're%20seeing%20today%20is%20Trump%20being%20much%20more%20aggressive%2C%26quot%3B%20Inker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20Trump's%20recent%20announcement%20of%2050%25%20tariffs%20on%20Brazil%20is%20%26quot%3Ban%20aggressive%20stance%20that%20sort%20of%20presumes%20you%20can%20do%20whatever%20you%20want%2C%20which%20is%20quite%20different%20from%20what%20we%20saw%20with%20the%20backdown%20from%20the%20Liberation%20Day%20tariffs%20when%20the%20bond%20market%20started%20going%20crazy%2C%26quot%3B%20Inker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20financial%20markets%20telling%20him%20to%20back%20off%2C%20he%20won't%20back%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20lately%20haven't%20been%20pricing%20in%20downside%20risks.%20The%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20and%20the%20Nasdaq%20hit%20all-time%20highs%20on%20Thursday%2C%20and%20valuations%20are%20high%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInker%20said%20that%20the%20benchmark%20index%20is%20probably%20close%20to%2040%25%20overvalued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US%20stock%20market%20looks%20quite%20expensive.%20Not%20as%20expensive%20as%20it%20was%20in%202000%2C%20but%20expensive%20relative%20to%20just%20about%20any%20other%20point%20in%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20Inker%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20its%20valuation%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20is%20basically%20at%20an%20all-time%20high.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20attractive%20opportunities%20within%20stocks%20at%20the%20moment%20are%20deep%20value%20stocks%20and%20developed-market%20stocks%20outside%20of%20the%20US%2C%20Inker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-taco-trade-selloff-tariffs-trump-backfire-gmo-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752311701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687152b33d5881a51c1d32f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-taco-trade-selloff-tariffs-trump-backfire-gmo-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Buying%20the%20dip%20during%20recent%20tariff%20volatility%20has%20been%20profitable%20for%20investors%2C%20but%20the%20TACO%20trade%20could%20ultimately%20backfire%2C%20GMO's%20Ben%20Inker%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40businessinsider.com%20(William%20Edwards)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-taco-trade-selloff-tariffs-trump-backfire-gmo-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sexual%20assault%20accused%20'lynched'%20in%20Arunachal%3A%20Dragged%20out%20of%20police%20station%3B%20dies%20in%20hospital%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752311573000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-122403812%2Cimgsize-319284.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsexual-assault-accused-lynched-in-arunachal-dragged-out-of-police-s