friendly%20locals%20and%20limited%20food%20choices.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20learning%20about%20unique%20cultures%20and%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20researching%20how%20to%20visit%20new%20countries%20in%20the%20most%20economical%20way%20possible.%20I've%20traveled%20to%20140%20countries%2C%20the%20majority%20as%20a%20solo%20traveler%20(though%20my%20Maltipoo%20dog%20Kimchi%20has%20accompanied%20me%20to%20eight%20countries%20and%20counting).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20latest%20adventure%20was%20my%20most%20logistically%20challenging%20yet%3A%20I%20went%20to%20Tuvalu%2C%20a%20small%20South%20Pacific%20island%20nation%20roughly%20halfway%20between%20Hawaii%20and%20Australia%2C%20that%20may%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpacific-islands-stunning-photos-sea-levels-way-of-life-climate-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompletely%20underwater%20by%202050%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETuvalu%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.explore.com%2F1500344%2Ftuvalu-least-visited-country-become-first-digital-virtual-nation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleast-visited%20country%20in%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20drawing%20only%20about%203%2C700%20travelers%20a%20year.%20With%20minimal%20infrastructure%2C%20little%20tourism%20promotion%2C%20and%20rising%20sea%20levels%20threatening%20its%20future%2C%20it%20remains%20largely%20off%20the%20global%20travel%20map.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20to%20other%20less-touristed%20destinations%20before%20%E2%80%94%20Bhutan%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20Algeria%20%E2%80%94%20that%20were%20complex%20due%20to%20hard-to-get%20visas%2C%20limited%20infrastructure%2C%20or%20safety%20concerns.%20Tuvalu%20presented%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20challenge%3A%20It's%20incredibly%20difficult%20to%20coordinate%20flights%2C%20and%20there's%20limited%20travel%20information%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20stayed%20in%20Tuvalu%20for%20three%20days%20and%20two%20nights.%20Here's%20what%20I%20wish%20I'd%20known%20before%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224f7da732-1bc4-4d9c-a096-237ed4e3de45%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20There's%20only%20one%20way%20in%20and%20out%20%E2%80%94%20and%20you%20can%20save%20on%20flights%20by%20being%20strategic%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20'aha'%20moment%20on%20the%20Tuvalu%20trip%20was%20when%20I%20told%20my%20driver%20I%20was%20afraid%20of%20missing%20my%20flight%2C%20and%20he%20reminded%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20plane%20hasn't%20landed%2C%20so%20don't%20worry.%26quot%3B%20Tuvalu%20is%20the%20only%20country%20I've%20visited%20where%2C%20each%20day%2C%20there's%20one%20plane%20in%20and%20one%20plane%20out%2C%20so%20your%20Flight%20Information%20Display%20System%20is%20literally%20the%20sky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETuvalu's%20only%20airport%20on%20the%20main%20island%2C%20Funafuti%20International%20Airport%20(FUN)%2C%20is%20served%20exclusively%20by%20Fiji%20Airways.%20Flights%20are%20very%20limited%20and%20currently%20include%20from%20Nadi%2C%20Fiji%2C%20once%20a%20week%20(Monday)%20and%20from%20Suva%2C%20Fiji%2C%20three%20times%20a%20week%20(Tuesday%2C%20Thursday%2C%20Saturday).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETravelers%20who%20aim%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvisited-went-to-every-country-in-the-world-favorites-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evisit%20all%20197%20countries%3C%2Fa%3E%20often%20plan%20ahead%20for%20their%20Tuvalu%20trip%2C%20knowing%20flights%20are%20difficult%20to%20coordinate.%20To%20avoid%20paying%20thousands%20of%20dollars%2C%20my%20recommendation%20is%20to%20wait%20for%20a%20Fiji%20Airways%20annual%20sale%20to%20book%20a%20round-trip%20flight%20from%20San%20Francisco%20(SFO)%20to%20Nadi.%20I've%20seen%20fares%20as%20low%20as%20%24700%20round-trip%2C%20which%20is%20a%20steal%2C%20as%20they're%20normally%20%241%2C000%2B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20flights%20from%20Fiji%20to%20Tuvalu%20were%20another%20%24700%20round-trip.%20It's%20advised%20to%20add%20a%20buffer%20day%20in%20Fiji%20before%20connecting%20to%20Tuvalu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221ff1a96c-2768-4130-a546-06eae78b66db%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Hotel%20bookings%20can%20get%20complicated%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20coordinating%20international%20travel%20in%20the%20South%20Pacific%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20account%20for%20the%20International%20Date%20Line.%20I%20departed%20San%20Francisco%20on%20a%20Sunday%20night%20and%20arrived%20at%20my%20destination%20Tuesday%20morning%20%E2%80%94%20only%20to%20realize%20I%20had%20mistakenly%20booked%20a%20hotel%20for%20Monday%20night.%20The%2011.5-hour%20flight%20effectively%20skipped%20Monday%20entirely%20due%20to%20the%20time%20zone%20shift%2C%20a%20common%20oversight%20when%20crossing%20the%20date%20line.%20(Luckily%2C%20the%20hotel%20was%20kind%20enough%20to%20accept%20a%20late%20cancel%20for%20me.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETuvalu%20has%20limited%20hotel%20rooms%20and%20%E2%80%94%20like%20the%20flights%20%E2%80%94%20they%20often%20sell%20out.%20In%20addition%20to%20tourists%2C%20construction%20crews%20from%20Australia%20and%20other%20nearby%20nations%20visit%20to%20support%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftcap.tv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETuvalu%20Coastal%20Adaptation%20Project%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20pumps%20sand%20from%20the%20seabed%20and%20deposits%20it%20along%20the%20shoreline%20to%20combat%20rising%20sea%20levels.%20I%20had%20to%20email%20several%20hotels%20before%20I%20found%20a%20vacancy%20at%20NiuEti%20Lodge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22928%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Niueti%20Lodge%2C%20a%20hotel%20in%20Tuvalu%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687175de85e81483682de700%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22862%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20NiuEti%20Lodge%20in%20Tuvalu%20is%20where%20the%20writer%20managed%20to%20book%20a%20stay.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Amanda%20Coffee%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ff239153-48b2-493c-8e55-14f90d247477%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Expect%20a%20crowd%20at%20the%20runway%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20a%20taxi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETuvalu's%20airport%20runway%20runs%20straight%20through%20the%20center%20of%20the%20island%2C%20doubling%20as%20a%20community%20space%20when%20no%20flights%20are%20scheduled.%20On%20off%20days%2C%20locals%20gather%20on%20the%20airstrip%20to%20play%20volleyball%2C%20soccer%2C%20and%20other%20sports%20%E2%80%94%20making%20the%20runway%20as%20much%20a%20playground%20as%20a%20point%20of%20entry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20landed%2C%20I%20hadn't%20realized%20there%20were%20no%20taxis.%20I%20asked%20how%20to%20get%20a%20ride%2C%20and%20without%20hesitation%2C%20a%20local%20offered%20to%20drive%20me%2C%20refusing%20any%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20we%20were%20about%20to%20leave%2C%20I%20spotted%20a%20small%20sign%20for%20my%20hotel%20and%20a%20woman%20calling%20my%20name.%20It%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20personalized%20pickup%20I%20hadn't%20expected%20%E2%80%94%20there%20was%20no%20mention%20of%20it%20in%20my%20hotel%20confirmation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22930%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22airport%20at%20Tuvalu%20with%20locals%20hanging%20out%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687176443d5881a51c1d380f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22780%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELocals%20at%20the%20Funafuti%20International%20Airport%20watch%20planes%20land.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Amanda%20Coffee%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2254723d27-0040-493a-a20d-97e627bb258d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Bring%20cash%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20we%20hit%20the%20road%2C%20I%20asked%20if%20there%20was%20an%20ATM.%20The%20airport%20staff%20excitedly%20showed%20me%20the%20ATM%20behind%20a%20red%20velvet%20curtain%20%E2%80%94%20they%20assumed%20I%20wanted%20to%20see%20the%20country's%20first%20ATM%20that%20was%20being%20unveiled%20and%20becoming%20operational%20later%20that%20month%2C%20not%20that%20I%20needed%20cash%20ASAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ATM%20wasn't%20yet%20working%2C%20so%20I%20had%20to%20visit%20the%20bank%20and%20Western%20Union%20myself%20money%2C%20as%20I%20didn't%20bring%20enough%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETuvalu%20only%20accepts%20Australian%20dollars%20(AUD)%2C%20so%20Fiji%20dollars%20from%20the%20ATM%20during%20your%20layover%20won't%20work%2C%20and%20credit%20cards%20are%20rarely%20accepted%2C%20even%20at%20hotels.%20It's%20best%20to%20bring%20AUD%20or%20carry%20extra%20USD%20or%20EUR%20to%20exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22894%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tuvalu's%20first%20ATM%20hadn't%20yet%20been%20unveiled%20in%20April%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687176c83d5881a51c1d3827%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22934%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETuvalu's%20first%20ATM%20hadn't%20yet%20been%20unveiled%20in%20April%202025.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Amanda%20Coffee%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fd3def56-70dd-485f-b415-603e4fa72da8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Food%20options%20are%20limited%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETuvalu%20imports%20nearly%20all%20of%20its%20food%2C%20and%20prices%20can%20be%20quite%20high%20%E2%80%94%20comparable%20to%20New%20York%20City%20%E2%80%94%20so%20budget%20accordingly.%20I%20ate%20most%20of%20my%20meals%20at%203T's%20restaurant%2C%20an%20open-air%20casual%20Chinese%20restaurant%20by%20the%20beach%20that%20specializes%20in%20fresh%20fish%20stir%20fry%20for%20%2411%20to%2015%20AUD.%20It%20was%20filled%20with%20locals%20enjoying%20the%20food%20washed%20down%20by%20Fanta%20Maracuj%C3%A1%2C%20a%20tangy%20passion%20fruit%20soda%20that's%20super%20popular%20on%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20grocery%20store%20was%20sparsely%20stocked%2C%20with%20one%20variety%20of%20many%20staples%20%E2%80%94%20Corn%20Flakes%20for%20%246%20AUD%20and%20Ritz%20crackers%20for%20%246%20AUD.%20The%20store%20was%20sold%20out%20of%20bananas%2C%20though%20I%20found%20a%20small%20market%20at%20the%20airport%20with%20a%20few%20bunches%20of%20local%20small%20bananas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228dab6d1c-43bf-4024-b811-fa883ce93cca%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Locals%20are%20incredibly%20welcoming%2C%20and%20it's%20fun%20to%20explore%20on%20foot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETuvaluans%20are%20kind%2C%20close-knit%2C%20and%20eager%20to%20help.%20You%20can%20walk%20nearly%20everywhere%3B%20the%20main%20island%20of%20Funafuti%20is%20only%200.93%20square%20miles%20of%20land%20area.%20Crime%20is%20rare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20felt%20safe%2C%20although%20there%20aren't%20many%20street%20lamps%20on%20the%20island%2C%20so%20plan%20ahead%20for%20a%20ride%20when%20coming%20back%20to%20your%20hotel%20at%20night.%20I%20was%20offered%20rides%20from%20locals%20more%20than%20once%2C%20even%20if%20I%20told%20them%20my%20destination%20was%20close%20by.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExploring%20on%20foot%20gives%20you%20a%20front%20row%20seat%20to%20locals%20fishing%2C%20playing%20with%20their%20dogs%2C%20and%20taking%20a%20dip%20in%20the%20ocean.%20Fun%20facts%20I%20learned%20when%20exploring%20the%20island%3A%20Tuvalu%20owns%20the%20.tv%20country%20code%20top-level%20domain%2C%20meaning%20it%20sells%20.tv%20to%20companies%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FPeacock.tv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeacock.tv%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FTwitch.tv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETwitch.tv%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20church%20services%20they%20offer%20is%20held%20in%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20local%20told%20me%20that%20Simon%20Kofe%2C%20Minister%20for%20Transport%2C%20Energy%2C%20Communications%2C%20and%20Innovation%2C%20was%20on%20my%20return%20flight%20to%20Fiji.%20He's%20well%20known%20for%20his%20advocacy%20work%20on%20climate%20change%2C%20including%20Tuvalu's%20project%20to%20mak