3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20fastened%20my%20seatbelt%20and%20secured%20the%20cabin%2C%20I%20was%20struck%20by%20the%20sense%20of%20responsibility%20that%20if%20I%20didn't%20do%20my%20job%20properly%20people%20could%20get%20hurt.%20Once%20the%20flight%20was%20over%2C%20I%20absolutely%20loved%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20leaving%20school%2C%20I%20trained%20in%20beauty%20therapy.%20I%20felt%20it%20was%20a%20skill%20you%20could%20take%20anywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20soon%20as%20I'd%20finished%2C%20I%20applied%20to%20work%20for%20easyJet%20and%20went%20straight%20into%20flying.%20I%20knew%20someone%20who%20had%20been%20cabin%20crew%2C%20and%20I'd%20always%20see%20them%20travelling.%20I%20wanted%20to%20explore%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20applied%20to%20work%20as%20cabin%20crew%20with%20easyJet%20based%20out%20of%20London%20Gatwick%20around%202013.%20After%20two%20years%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20experience%20the%20real%20deal%20of%20cabin%20crew%2C%20with%20longer%20layovers%2C%20so%20I%20applied%20to%20work%20for%20British%20Airways%2C%20where%20I%20stayed%20for%20five%20years.%20I%20worked%20for%20an%20independent%20private%20jet%20company%20before%20joining%20Emirates%20and%20relocating%20to%20Dubai%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20so%20much%20more%20to%20cabin%20crew%20than%20serving%20food%20and%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20responsible%20for%20the%20security%20search%20of%20the%20aircraft%2C%20the%20safety%20equipment%20checks.%20There%20are%20often%20medical%20situations%20on%20board%2C%20and%20we%20have%20to%20know%20what%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cf4b0c5e-09d3-4ae1-ae5b-eb02e2700ee1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeauty%20therapist%20to%20flight%20attendant%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20other%20jobs%2C%20you%20submit%20your%20CV%20online%2C%20but%20airline%20companies%20have%20different%20requirements%20before%20you're%20invited%20for%20an%20interview.%20With%20easyJet%2C%20there%20were%20maths%20and%20English%20tests%20and%20customer%20service-based%20scenario%20questions.%20There's%20a%20height%20test%20to%20make%20sure%20you're%20tall%20enough%20to%20reach%20the%20overhead%20lockers%2C%20and%20you%20must%20be%20able%20to%20swim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20got%20the%20role%2C%20I%20completed%20training%2C%20which%20included%20treading%20water%2C%20going%20down%20the%20slide%2C%20and%20pulling%20yourself%20up%20into%20the%20slide%20raft%20from%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20the%20hours%20were%20a%20massive%20adjustment.%20In%20beauty%2C%20you%20tend%20to%20work%20a%20typical%209-to-5.%20Whereas%20at%20easyJet%2C%20I%20was%20setting%20an%20alarm%20for%202%20or%203%20a.m.%20Your%20schedule%20can%20vary%20so%20much%20as%20a%20flight%20attendant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20average%2C%20I%20get%20about%2010%20days%20off%20a%20month%2C%20and%20we%20also%20have%20rest%20days%20before%20a%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20background%20in%20beauty%20has%20come%20in%20handy.%20At%20Emirates%2C%20it's%20a%20requirement%20to%20wear%20basic%20makeup%2C%20along%20with%20the%20signature%20red%20lips%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20part%20of%20the%20uniform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2238d24df2-bf27-4194-ab2b-9d24bba36e06%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoving%20to%20Dubai%20for%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20moved%20to%20Dubai%20in%202022.%20At%20first%2C%20I%20lived%20in%20accommodation%20provided%20by%20Emirates%2C%20which%20also%20sponsors%20our%20work%20permits%20and%20visas.%20Now%2C%20I%20live%20in%20my%20own%20apartment%2C%20which%20I%20can%20afford%20thanks%20to%20Emirates'%20live-out%20allowance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20lots%20of%20perks%2C%20including%20a%20tax-free%20salary%2C%20transport%20to%20work%2C%20and%20a%20platinum%20card%20which%20gives%20us%20free%20access%20to%20beach%20clubs%20and%20discounts%20at%20shops%20and%20restaurants%20here%3A%20it%20might%20be%2025%25%20off%20the%20bill%2C%20free%20entry%20to%20a%20nice%20hotel%2C%20or%2010%25%20off%20in%20a%20clothes%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20been%20to%20Dubai%20on%20holiday%20and%20enjoyed%20it%2C%20but%20since%20I've%20moved%2C%20I've%20found%20that%20it%20is%20my%20No.%201%20city%3A%20it's%2024%2F7%2C%20there%20are%20always%20things%20to%20do%20and%20places%20to%20explore%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20big%20expat%20community.%20It's%20the%20perfect%20base%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20be%20tough%20being%20away%20from%20home%2C%20but%20on%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20my%20family%20is%20spread%20out%2C%20so%20I%20feel%20like%20it's%20enabled%20me%20to%20stay%20connected%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20allocated%20routes%20on%20our%20rota%2C%20but%20we%20can%20bid%20for%20specific%20flights%20or%20swap%20among%20crew%20as%20long%20as%20it%20fits%20the%20allocated%20times.%20I'll%20switch%20to%20UK%20flights%20to%20see%20my%20mum%2C%20or%20Sweden%20in%20the%20summer%20to%20catch%20up%20with%20my%20brother.%20The%20Australia%20flight%20to%20Sydney%20allows%20me%20to%20see%20friends%20and%20cousins%20over%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a449355b-5cb5-4398-9c3b-7f646870ea23%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeeting%20new%20people%20is%20my%20favorite%20part%20of%20the%20job%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20though%2C%20the%20best%20part%20of%20the%20job%20is%20meeting%20different%20people%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20visited%20more%20than%2050%20countries%2C%20and%20I%20still%20haven't%20flown%20to%20all%20the%20destinations%20that%20we%20fly%20to.%20It%20opens%20your%20mind%20and%20your%20horizons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20never%20know%20who%20you're%20flying%20with%20%E2%80%94%20every%20day%20I%20go%20to%20work%2C%20I%20meet%20new%20people%2C%20do%20new%20things.%20You%20learn%20how%20to%20speak%20to%20all%20types%20of%20people%20and%20to%20be%20patient.%20I%20treat%20my%20passengers%20as%20if%20they%20were%20my%20mum%20or%20my%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYears%20ago%2C%20I%20had%20a%20situation%20where%20a%20woman%20was%20projectile%20vomiting%20and%20unexpectedly%20had%20a%20fit.%20She%20came%20round%2C%20but%20all%20her%20clothes%20were%20in%20the%20hold.%20My%20mum%20had%20given%20me%20a%20tracksuit%20for%20Christmas%2C%20which%20was%20in%20my%20overnight%20bag%2C%20so%20I%20gave%20her%20my%20clothes.%20Later%2C%20she%20wrote%20in%20to%20thank%20me.%20These%20kinds%20of%20experiences%2C%20when%20you%20help%20or%20connect%20with%20someone%2C%20stand%20out%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20I%20thought%20I'd%20do%20this%20for%20a%20year%2C%20but%20here%20I%20am%2012%20years%20later%2C%20still%20flying.%20It%20still%20has%20that%20novelty%20because%20every%20day%20is%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20when%20I%20look%20out%20of%20the%20window%20and%20we're%20flying%20over%20the%20mountains%2C%20I%20think%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20really%20is%20amazing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femirates-flight-attendant-lives-dubai-perks-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752311341000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687102753d5881a51c1d255b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femirates-flight-attendant-lives-dubai-perks-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Emirates%20flight%20attendant%20shares%20how%20her%20initial%20training%20in%20beauty%20therapy%20complements%20her%20aviation%20career%2C%20job%20perks%2C%20and%20living%20in%20Dubai.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Emma%20Magnus)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A50%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femirates-flight-attendant-lives-dubai-perks-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDon't%20Jump%20To%20Conclusions%26quot%3B%3A%20Aviation%20Minister%20On%20Air%20India%20Crash%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Ciframe%20data-src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv