or%20to%20producing%20Mahua-based%20pickles%20and%20sweets.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fjharkhand-samvad-4-1752233544.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fjharkhand-samvad-4-1752233544-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fjharkhand-samvad-4-1752233544-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fjharkhand-samvad-4-1752233544-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fjharkhand-samvad-4-1752233544-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-468102%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20guidance%20from%20SAMVAD%20and%20Climate%20Asia%2C%20villagers%20shifted%20from%20brewing%20liquor%20to%20producing%20Mahua-based%20pickles%20and%20sweets.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20was%20once%20primarily%20used%20for%20liquor%20has%20shifted%20towards%20boosting%20the%20villagers%E2%80%99%20livelihood%20and%20improving%20health.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESAMVAD%20is%20now%20working%20towards%20making%20cookies%20and%20exploring%20other%20innovative%20uses%20of%20the%20forest%20produce%2C%20including%20disposable%20plates%20with%20Sal%20Tree%20leaves%2C%20and%20cocoon%20rearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20SAMVAD%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20revolved%20around%20self-governance%2C%20self-reliance%2C%20and%20protection%20of%20tribal%20dignity.%20This%20was%20implemented%20through%20organic%20farming%20and%20organising%20gram%20sabhas.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20us%2C%20the%20forest%20is%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20reflects%20Ghanshyam.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20save%20our%20forests%2C%20we%20save%20our%20environment%2C%20water%2C%20and%20lives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECollaboration%20with%20Climate%20Asi