n%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20ease%20the%20financial%20burden%2C%20Poonam%20took%20on%20odd%20jobs%2C%20such%20as%20washing%20aircraft%2C%20working%20shifts%20in%20coffee%20shops%2C%20and%20anything%20that%20helped%20her%20stay%20in%20training.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20glamorous%2C%20but%20every%20little%20bit%20helped.%20Every%20shift%20got%20me%20closer%20to%20the%20sky.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20her%20undying%20spirit%20did%20pay%20off%20%E2%80%94%20not%20all%20at%20once%2C%20but%20over%20time%2C%20in%20the%20hours%20she%20carved%20out%20between%20flights%20and%20studies.%20While%20flying%20with%20Jet%20Airways%2C%20she%20kept%20up%20with%20her%20coursework%2C%20often%20catching%20up%20on%20assignments%20between%20layovers%20or%20after%20long%20shifts.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy%20to%20keep%20pace%20with%20both%20worlds%2C%20but%20she%20kept%20at%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20finally%20graduated%2C%20she%20had%20not%20only%20completed%20her%20degree%2C%20but%20also%20she%20had%20topped%20her%20university.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20people%20in%C2%A0%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EJet%20Airways%20started%20calling%20her%20the%20%E2%80%9CGolden%20Girl%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENavigating%20cockpits%2C%20controls%20and%20confidence%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsk%20her%20about%20her%20first%20time%20flying%20a%20plane%2C%20and%20her%20eyes%20light%20up.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20surreal.%20Sitting%20in%20the%20cockpit%2C%20gripping%20the%20controls%20%E2%80%94%20It%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20finally%20where%20I%20belonged.%20As%20the%20plane%20lifted%20off%2C%20I%20could%20feel%20my%20whole%20life%20changing%20in%20a%20moment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Poonam%E2%80%99s%20hard%20work%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20always%20welcomed%20with%20clear%20skies.%20There%20were%20moments%20of%20doubt%20and%20exhaustion%2C%20and%20of%20questioning%20her%20ability%20and%20choices.%